          name: "Mortimer, J.H., Nosko, C., & Sorensen, A. (2012). 'Supply Responses to Digital Distribution: Recorded Music and Live Performances.' Information Economics and Policy, 24(1), 3–14.",
          url: "https://doi.org/10.1016/j.infoecopol.2012.01.005"
