          name: "Wikström, P. (2013). The Music Industry: Music in the Cloud (2nd ed.). Polity Press. Chapter 5: Music Industry Intermediaries.",
          url: "https://www.politybooks.com/bookdetail?book_slug=the-music-industry-music-in-the-cloud--9780745653037"
